---
import UseCases from "./UseCases";
---

<section id="use-cases" class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1240px] px-6 sm:px-10 pt-20 sm:pt-24 pb-20 sm:pb-24">
  <div class="section-rule mb-10">
    <span>§ 05a · Use cases</span>
  </div>

  <header class="max-w-[760px] mb-12" data-reveal>
    <h2 class="display text-[color:var(--color-ink-50)]" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 56px);">
      What it looks like <span class="display-accent">in your Claude Code session.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-[15px] leading-[1.6] text-[color:var(--color-ink-300)] max-w-[640px]">
      Four canonical moments: a fresh SaaS scaffold, adding analytics to an existing
      app, rotating a leaked token, and picking a provider from the catalog. Each
      shows the actual chat turn, the <code class="mono text-[color:var(--color-ink-100)]">stack</code>
      command Claude invokes, and the terminal output your agent will see.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div data-reveal>
    <UseCases client:visible />
  </div>
</section>
